Liquid I.V.® Hydration Multiplier® is a great-tasting, Non-GMO electrolyte drink mix powered by Cellular Transport Technology (CTT)®️ to hydrate faster and more efficiently than water alone. Cellular Transport Technology, or CTT®, is the breakthrough delivery system used in all of our products, designed to enhance rapid absorption of water and other key ingredients into the bloodstream. Typically, when you drink fluids, they pass through the entire digestive system, losing water before your body can absorb it. CTT® uses a precise ratio of sodium, glucose and potassium to create an osmotic force that allows water to be delivered to the bloodstream earlier on in the digestive system. Think of CTT® as an expedited water delivery system in your body. The result? Feel better, faster. 1 stick contains 3x the electrolytes of traditional sports drinks with 5 essential vitamins.
No Artificial Ingredients
Convenient, Travel-Friendly, Single-Serving Packets
5 Essential Vitamins: B3, B5, B6, B12 and Vitamin C
2-2.5x faster hydration than water alone

ProductName: Waiakea Volcanic Water - Case Of 2-6/33.8FZ
ProductSubCategory: Waiakea Volcanic Water - Case Of 2-6/33.8FZ
Description:
Waiākea’s mission is to provide naturally healthy, delicious, Hawaiian volcanic water with as little impact as possible, while contributing to and promoting conservation and access to clean water and education for people in need throughout the world. This is embodied by Waiākea’s slogan “Drink Healthy, Drink Sustainably, Drink Ethically”.
In accordance with the Hawaiian practice and notion of “malama i ka ‘aina”, meaning “to respect and care for the land”, Waiākea is also proud to be the first American premium bottled water and beverage to be certified CarbonNeutral for its variety of eco-initiatives, including using 100% RPET packaging, sustainable sourcing, and its regional reforestation projects.
We love what our brand represents. From the high standards it sets, to the active lifestyle it promotes, to the lives it changes. With your help we will continue to strive for the summit- kulia i ka nu’u.

ProductName: Nestle® Abuelita Mexican Hot Chocolate Tablets

Nestle Abuelita Mexican Hot Chocolate Drink Tablets let you treat your family to a delightfully frothy and flavorful cup of authentic Mexican hot chocolate drink. The convenient hot chocolate drink tablets make it easy to make a delicious cup of Mexican hot cocoa drink mix at any time of day. Once opened, store unused Mexican hot chocolate drink mix tablets in a tightly sealed container in a cool, dry place.

For almost 5,000 years, tea drinkers around the world have embraced its delicious taste, enlivening aroma, and revitalizing flavors. Lipton Green Tea is picked while young, giving it a fresher, lighter flavor characterized by a crisp flavor and natural earthiness. We think our green tea blend is ideal for focusing and reviving. Try it hot and fresh to start your day or iced and refreshing for a mid-day cool down or snack break. For balanced flavor, we recommend steeping Lipton Green Tea in water that’s just under boiling, and only for two minutes so it retains all those lovely, fresh, and energizing flavors. Plus, since each cup of tea is 99.5% water, it helps keep the body hydrated and balanced.

With the velvety texture and creaminess of Califia Farms Extra Creamy Oatmilk, you won’t miss dairy milk again.It’s the milkiest of all the plant milks. ProductName: ReaLemon® 100% Lemon Juice
ProductSubCategory: ReaLemon® 100% Lemon Juice
Description:
When you’re looking for a splash of lemon or lime juice, nothing beats ReaLemon and ReaLime. Made with 100% lemon and lime juice from concentrate, you get the benefit of the great taste of real juice without the hassle of cutting into fresh lemons or limes. First introduced in Chicago in 1934 by Irving Swartzburg, ReaLemon and ReaLime have been trusted brands that deliver only the highest quality of lemon and lime juice. ReaLemon and ReaLime are space-saving kitchen sidekicks, ideal for adding a delicious twist of lemon or lime to your favorite seafood and poultry recipes. Although they’re both great for use in a variety of marinades, they have their unique uses as well. Use ReaLemon to brighten up both hot and cold beverages or use ReaLime to add a bright splash of flavor to salads and dressings. When you want the real taste of real lemon or lime, simply reach for ReaLemon and ReaLime.
REAL FLAVOR: Made with 100% lemon and lime juice from concentrate
FRESH TASTE: Get the taste of real juice without the hassle of cutting into fresh lemons or limes
NATURALLY GOOD: ReaLemon and ReaLime are caffeine-free, gluten-free and sodium-free
FOOD ENHANCER: ReaLemon and ReaLime are space-saving kitchen sidekicks, adding a delicious twist of lemon or lime to your favorite seafood, poultry and marinades

Infused with crisp spearmint leaves, fresh lemon verbena, and zesty lemongrass, this organic green tea blend will kick off your mornings on a high note. And with just the right amount of caffeine, it’s the perfect pick-me-up for those slow afternoons. Comes packaged with 16 individual tea bags for your sipping pleasure, and it's Kosher, Fair Trade and Non-GMO Project Verified. Simply bring 8 fl oz of fresh, filtered water to a boil, pour over the tea bag, steep for 3 minutes, and bam! You’re ready to take that first invigorating sip (and the second, third, and fourth...we could go on forever.) At TAZO®, we’re not just a tea company. We’re a group of tea-obsessed people on a mission to challenge the status quo. This doesn’t stop at exciting, new tea blends; it continues with making the world a better place. That means investing in regenerative growing practices. Stepping up for environmental justice. And shining a spotlight on important issues (like the climate crisis) to help our communities—and the planet. So choose your favorite blend, brew a cup, and let's stir things up.
TAZO® Regenerative – Organic ZEN is an invigorating green tea blend
This organic green tea blend pairs crisp spearmint leaves with lemon verbena and zesty lemongrass
Our green tea is brewed with just enough caffeine to wake you up without throwing off your groove
Easy prep: just bring fresh, filtered water to a boil, pour over tea bag, and steep for 3 minutes
Our Kosher and Non-GMO tea comes conveniently packaged in 16 individual tea bags
USDA Organic, NonGMO Project Verified, Rainforest Alliance Certified, made from Fair Trade Certified ingredients

ProductName: Meyenberg - Goat Milk Whole Powdered - Case Of 6-12 Oz
ProductSubCategory: Meyenberg - Goat Milk Whole Powdered - Case Of 6-12 Oz
Description: More people drink worldwide drink goat milk than any other dairy milk! Since 1934, Meyenberg has been bringing the goodness of goat milk to people across the country. Easier to digest than cow milk, and much less processed than plant ‘milk,’ goat milk is a delicious and nutritious alternative. It’s a good source of complete protein, healthy fats, and minerals like calcium, magnesium, and potassium. We all know that goats are adorable, fun-loving animals to have around, but they also have a much smaller environmental ‘hoofprint’ than other livestock raised for dairy. Not only do they need less water per gallon of milk produced, but they also produce much less methane than dairy cows per kilogram of body weight! Our goat milk powder can be used in recipes, or mixed with water to make fluid milk. Packed in convenient, resealable pouches, and featuring a long shelf life of 2 ½ years unopened.

Liquid IV Hydration Multiplier Electrolyte Drink Mix offers a refreshing way to hydrate that's not only more efficient than drinking plain water, it's more flavorful as well! Formulated with a specialized ratio of sodium citrate (from ascorbic acid) and cane sugar (non-GMO), each powder stick provides an optimized dose of natural electrolytes like dipotassium phosphate and potassium citrate. These electrolytes work together with ingredients such as naturally occurring dextrose to promote a faster and more efficient absorption of fluid into the bloodstream through a process known as Cellular Transport Technology. Along with providing greater hydration than the usual sports drinks, Liquid IV Hydration Multiplier Electrolyte Drink Mix enhances your water with a delicious strawberry flavor sweetened with extracts of stevia leaf and created using only natural fruit juices. Enjoy your hydration knowing it includes the added nutrition of B vitamins and vitamin C, all in a convenient stick packet that can be used almost anywhere!
Boosts energy with B vitamins and vitamin C
Supports more efficient hydration with natural electrolytes
Features Cellular Transport Technology for improved absorption
Gluten Free, Vegan, Vegetarian, Non-GMO

Description: Hormel's Thick and Easy water is a convenient liquid option for individuals with dysphagia. Aspiration is a common problem when people with dysphagia drink thin liquids. Therefore, it is essential to add thickened beverages to the diet. With a nectar consistency, Hormel thickened water is viscous enough to reduce the chances of it flowing into the airway. This great-tasting clear hydrolyte thickened water is lemon-flavor and contains other natural flavors. Rated IDDSI-2 by the International Dysphagia Diet Standardisation Initiative, every serving has a reliable mildly-thick consistency. Fortified with electrolytes like sodium, the Hormel thickened water releases 98% of the available fluid after consumption for optimal hydration. There are only 5 calories per serving, making the beverage compatible with weight-loss diets and helping to maintain a healthy body weight. The thickened water comes in an easy-to-handle 46-ounce plastic bottle with a twist-off lid for quick opening.

This doesn’t stop at exciting, new tea blends; it continues with making the world a better place. That means investing in regenerative growing practices. Stepping up for environmental justice. ProductName: Fre Non-Alcoholic Red
ProductSubCategory: Fre Non-Alcoholic Red
Description: Fre Red Blend offers a deep ruby color and ripe, black cherry scented aromas. Smooth and rich, it offers plenty of bright, grape, and cherry fruit with an intriguing smoky flavor. Fre Red Blend ends with a long, fruity, lingering finish. This alcohol removed wine is delightful on its own or paired with salmon, turkey, chicken and ham dishes, as well as pasta, pizza, and grilled meats. Fre Red Blend is produced using the revolutionary spinning cone column. The spinning cone facilitates the removal and safeguarding of fragile wine aromas and flavors at low temperatures, then removes the alcohol at slightly higher temperatures. The wine essences are then reintroduced to the dealcoholized base wine and blended with unfermented grape juice. The finished product is a rich, delicious beverage with the characteristic aromas and flavors of premium wine. Fre Red Blend is an ideal choice for red wine drinkers seeking quality, alcohol-removed alternatives for meals, parties, and special occasions.

Liquid IV Hydration Multiplier Electrolyte Drink Mix offers a refreshing way to hydrate that's not only more efficient than drinking plain water, it's more flavorful as well! Enjoy your hydration with the added nutrition of B vitamins and healthful vitamin C, all in a convenient packet that can travel with you almost anywhere!

Description: There are few places on earth as enchanting as Darjeeling, a small but vibrant town in the Indian state of West Bengal. Located in the foothills of the Himalayan Mountains, the high elevation gardens and sloped terrain of this region produce distinctive teas that are harvested in three growing seasons called "flushes."First Flush teas are harvested in March following the spring rains and have a fresh, lively taste. Second Flush teas are harvested in June and have a mellow, muscatel flavour. Autumn Flush teas are rich and smooth, but bolder in flavour. Our Darjeeling combines teas from the 1st and 2nd Flushes to yield a sophisticated tea with a woody aroma and slightly dry, delicate taste.
